query: SELECT id, studentId, personalId, DATE_FORMAT(scheduledAt, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i') as scheduledAt, status, deletedAt FROM sessions WHERE studentId = 1 AND status IN ('scheduled', 'confirmed') AND deletedAt IS NULL ORDER BY scheduledAt DESC LIMIT 20;
